data.description: Welcome to this serene, meticulously maintained condo w beautiful water views in an active community. Breathtaking landscaping & backing up to Eagle Creek, this property boasts vaulted ceilings & bright natural light throughout. You enter through a foyer that leads you into an open concept kitchen & living room, & out to a private deck. One bedroom opens w dbl doors, & the master has an attached bath. Some of the amazing features are the bamboo flooring, updated bathrooms & kitchen, '23 water heater & '22 furnace, & a private storage unit. It is the definition of turn key! Walking distance to beach access of Eagle Creek Reservoir, or Rick's Boatyard, & minutes from 465, this location is perfect! Check out more info in the supplements!
